    "created_at": "2016-10-27T16:45:24Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-10-27T16:45:24Z",
    "body": "> Is there another way to use accelerator from Browser window without adding menu?\n\nYes, there's https://github.com/parro-it/electron-localshortcut, a module to register/unregister a keyboard shortcut locally to a BrowserWindow instance, without using a Menu.\n"
